1.title: Slumber Party Panic/Trouble in Lumpy Space
1.plot: Slumber Party Panic: Princess Bubblegum and Finn are doing experiments in a graveyard when they accidentally create candy zombies. / Trouble in Lumpy Space: Jake starts to turn lumpy after being bitten by Lumpy Space Princess.

2.title: Hot to the Touch/Five Short Graybles
2.plot: Hot to the Touch: Finn goes on a quest to prove that Flame Princess isn't evil. / Five Short Graybles: A series of short stories all centered around the five senses.

3.title: Princess Cookie/Card Wars
3.plot: Princess Cookie: Finn and Jake are called on to solve a Candy Kingdom crisis when a cookie takes over. / Card Wars: Finn and Jake embark on an epic game of Card Quest.

4.title: My Two Favorite People/Memories of Boom Boom Mountain
4.plot: My Two Favorite People: Jake tries to broker peace between Lady Rainicorn and Finn. / Memories of Boom Boom Mountain: Finn gets caught up in trying to make everyone happy.

imdb.plot outline: Here's a list of ten awesome things you'll find in Adventure Time Volume 10! The Finn Sword, a runaway Sea Lard, Charlie plays Card Wars, Battle of the Bands, Ice Kingdom secrets, artistic pancakes, Cinnamon Bun, Normal Man and, of course, Finn & Jake!
